                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="4">
                                <para>(464- R12), 57F to ground.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="5">
                                <para>&#60;1 ohm.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="6">
