                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="7">
                                <para>Locate open or poor connection in circuit 57F, then repair.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para>5.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>Off</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3">
                                <para>With a good bulb installed, measure resistance between cluster (72) cavity 2 and
                                    cavity 18
                                    <hotlnk document="s08245x_27.xml" xrefid="f0824519">(Figure 19)</hotlnk>.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="4">
                                <para>(73), cavity 2 to cavity 5.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="5">
